<p>The highly anticipated CES pre-registered media list was sent out on November 1, 2012 to exhibitors hosting CES press events on-site. The list will also be posted to CESweb.org on December 1 for all other exhibitors&ndash; mark your calendar! All you need to access the list is your CES Exhibitor ID. Don&rsquo;t wait until you&rsquo;re at the show to get in front of the media, share your exciting news before it starts. <strong>New for 2013: Exhibitors can filter the pre-registered media list by product category. </strong>Take full advantage of this new feature and pull targeted media lists to target media covering your product categories.</p>
