<p><em>Variety </em>will be producing printed dailies for the 2013 International CES, dedicated to Entertainment Matters programming, news, events, announcements and special features. You will have firsthand access to the most important news and announcements impacting the entertainment industry at CES. Advertising is available &ndash; front cover and premium spots as well as standard ad units in the book. 10,000 copies will be distributed daily between January 8-11, 2012, and in addition to the printed dailies onsite, over 27,000 Variety subscribers will have access to view digital editions online.<br />
<br />
For inquiries, please contact <em>Variety&#39;s</em> Publishing Director, Linda Buckley-Bruno at <a href="mailto:linda.buckley@variety.com" target="_blank">linda.buckley@variety.com</a> or 323-617-9429.</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="783"><span style="display: none">Tell Us About Your Celebrity Guest Appearances & Special Events </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Tell Us About Your Celebrity Guest Appearances & Special Events </div><br/>

<p>Is your company planning a special concert with a popular chart-topper? How about an autograph session with Hollywood royalty or a product demonstration with a sports legend? If so, let us know! We can assist you with special security arrangements, staging requirements, catering requests or anything else you need to make your event a success. We&rsquo;ll help you publicize it by including details on CESweb.org, in a news release and in the press room. Many exhibitors that host special events or celebrities choose not to announce their events until closer to the show and we will certainly accommodate those requests. We will also be happy to designate it as strictly invitation-only.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.cesweb.org/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Documents/Exhibitor/Exhibitor%20PR%20Kit/Celebrity_Special_Events_Form.pdf" target="_blank">Fill out our 2013 CES Celebrity Appearance/Special Event Promotion Request Form</a><strong> and return it to </strong><a href="mailto:PRcontacts@CE.org" target="_blank">PRcontacts@CE.org</a><strong> or fax to 703-907-8112.</strong></p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="784"><span style="display: none">Special Advertising Opportunity </span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Special Advertising Opportunity </div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/newsletter/attendee/i3.gif"/>
<p>Make a splash at CES by advertising in the inaugural edition of the Consumer Electronics Association&rsquo;s (CEA)&reg;&nbsp;new magazine, <em>It Is Innovation (i3)</em>. <em>i3</em> will launch at the 2013 International CES and will showcase all aspects of innovation in technology, policy, business and engineering in the consumer technology industry.&nbsp;Gain exposure with those who care the most about innovation &ndash; attendees at the 2013 CES. <em>i3</em> has exclusive distribution to areas of the show that no other publication receives, including 3,000 exhibitor booths, inside press bags, CEA member lounges, executive suites, the press rooms, the international reception, the VIP lunchroom, CES Unveiled and the Innovations Award Showcase and of course, the pub bins. Purchase your ads now through November 30. Contact <a href="mailto:dcole@ce.org" target="_blank">Dan Cole</a> today for more information about special introductory pricing.</p>
