<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/CES.jpg"/>
<p>Make sure you bookmark <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/" target="_blank">CESweb.org</a> for up to the minute breaking news on the latest stories surrounding the 2013 International CES. Our <a href="http://cesweb.org/News.aspx" target="_blank">News</a> section is dedicated to breaking headlines, such as our latest <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/News/CES-Press-Releases/CES-Press-Release.aspx?NodeID=11d4b96f-0fcc-477a-8cc9-ddb9158115a0" target="_blank">show announcement:</a> the 2013 International CES&reg; is the largest app event in the world. Look out for other important information posted front and center on the homepage, along with links to CEA&rsquo;s Digital Dialogue Blog, relevant videos and photos and our social media platforms.</p>
